<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
    <title>Agenda do Dia</title>
    <style>
      body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; }
      .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }
      .header { background-color: #10b981; color: white; padding: 20px; text-align: center; border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0; }
      .content { background-color: #f9fafb; padding: 30px; border-radius: 0 0 8px 8px; }
      .appointment-box { background-color: white; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb; border-radius: 8px; padding: 20px; margin: 20px 0; }
      .appointment-time { font-size: 18px; font-weight: bold; color: #3b82f6; margin-bottom: 10px; }
      .appointment-details { margin-bottom: 10px; }
      .appointment-label { font-weight: bold; color: #6b7280; }
      .appointment-value { color: #111827; }
      .footer { text-align: center; margin-top: 30px; color: #6b7280; font-size: 14px; }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="header">
        <h1>Agenda do Dia</h1>
        <p><%= @date.strftime('%d/%m/%Y') %></p>
      </div>

      <div class="content">
        <p>Olá <%= @professional.name %>,</p>

        <p>Aqui está sua agenda para hoje:</p>

        <% if @appointments.any? %>
          <% @appointments.each do |appointment| %>
            <div class="appointment-box">
              <div class="appointment-time">
                <%= appointment.scheduled_at.strftime('%H:%M') %>
              </div>
              <div class="appointment-details">
                <div class="appointment-label">Paciente:</div>
                <div class="appointment-value"><%= appointment.patient&.name || 'Não informado' %></div>
              </div>
              <div class="appointment-details">
                <div class="appointment-label">Tipo:</div>
                <div class="appointment-value"><%= appointment.appointment_type.humanize %></div>
              </div>
              <div class="appointment-details">
                <div class="appointment-label">Duração:</div>
                <div class="appointment-value"><%= appointment.duration_minutes %> minutos</div>
              </div>
              <div class="appointment-details">
                <div class="appointment-label">Prioridade:</div>
                <div class="appointment-value"><%= appointment.priority.humanize %></div>
              </div>
              <% if appointment.notes.present? %>
                <div class="appointment-details">
                  <div class="appointment-label">Observações:</div>
                  <div class="appointment-value"><%= simple_format(appointment.notes) %></div>
                </div>
              <% end %>
            </div>
          <% end %>
        <% else %>
          <div class="appointment-box">
            <p>Nenhuma consulta agendada para hoje.</p>
          </div>
        <% end %>

        <p>Bom trabalho!</p>

        <p>Atenciosamente,<br>Equipe IntegrarPlus</p>
      </div>

      <div class="footer">
        <p>Este é um email automático, por favor não responda.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
